import React from "react"; import { evaluate } from 'mathjs'; import { Calculator } from "./Calculator"; export class CalculatorDisplay extends React.Component{ constructor(props){ super(props); this.changeCalculate = this.changeCalculate.bind(this); this.sumCalculate = this.sumCalculate.bind(this); this.clearCalculate = this.clearCalculate.bind(this); this.changeCharge = this.changeCharge.bind(this); } changeCalculate(e){ this.props.changeCalculate(e); } sumCalculate(e){ this.props.sumCalculate(e); } clearCalculate(e){ this.props.clearCalculate(e); } changeCharge(e){ this.props.changeCharge(e); } render(){ return(
{ display }
); } }
